Name: The President
About the game: You are Tom Reed, the youngest President of the Republic of Dora and the rising star of the Democratic Party. The future of the country is in your hands. Now you have the power. During your career you will have to make choices and tough decisions. Learn to live under pressure. You will deal with all sorts of people. So doubt everything. Choose the right allies. You will need them to win the elections and to stay alive. Never forget that defeat is not an option. Always remember who you are. You are the President.
